room_title: Escape room "Dorm Room Daze" by Urban Enigmas in Athens
room_address: 10 Huntington Road Unit B70 Athens, GA 30606
room_description: Kickoff to the big game against conference rivals is in an hour, and your tickets are nowhere to be found. You quickly realize that during last night's get together at the dorm, some of the attendees decided it would be fun to prank you and hide the tickets. You have 60 minutes to follow the clues that were left behind by the pranksters, find the tickets, and make it to the game. Or face missing the biggest game of the year!
